    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="633651537">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-633651537" class="vote-count">11</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-633651537" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="633651537">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wangtianou/">_区鸟</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-02-14</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">陈丹青太过频繁的推介，就不细看。且被引用有好多类似“微薄疯传体”的过聪明句子，还以为木心先生也是便秘积攒型白痴，结果，一读被震住了，那些傻逼们苦思冥想好几天才做得的一句聪明句子，先生他随口就来，在我看来天马行空的瑰丽想象和奇崛比喻，先生随手拈来，写得真真个的好</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1033478083">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1033478083" class="vote-count">6</span>
