  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5224738/" class="title-link">悼木心</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5224738"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Catherine1989/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3078893-31.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Catherine1989/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">大担忧家</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-12-22"
      class="main-meta">2011-12-22 00:21:32</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5224738_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  从来没有那么一个人，让我叹服地哑口无言。他刻薄，却刻薄地让人满心熨帖。  2007年我去乌镇，还不知道他，只是乌镇在我心里几乎是个水里的剪影，温柔地不像话。后来知道了，还知道他回了乌镇的孙家花园，一直想旧地重游，隔着栅栏看看他的院子就好，来不及成行，这个惦念就断...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5224738/#comments">(53回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">289有用 / 13没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5224738_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5224738_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2623319">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2623319/" class="title-link">旧时月影，依稀如梦</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2623319"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/7306389/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u7306389-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/7306389/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">嵇之蓠</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-10-26"
      class="main-meta">2009-10-26 21:14:52</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2623319_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这次新版，集八册为一套。纸张略逊旧版。木心的文章在大陆出版，现今已是一大事。都说他迟到，其实应算姗姗来迟。对他的文学，争议不小。我是喜欢他的文字的，因其为文态度，运用文字的功力，这都让人心里一惊。竟有人这样写作？！有论者评“旧文人的做派”，褒贬之意自在其中...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2623319/#comments">(10回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">39有用 / 5没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2623319_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2623319_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
